OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump has reportedly
OL,7,Ftold aides he would be willing to end
OL,8,Fthe war in Iran even if the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz remains largely closed, the
OL,10,FWall Street Journal reported late
OL,11,FMonday.
OL,13,FThe Strait, an essential waterway
OL,14,Fthrough which a fifth of the world's
OL,15,Foil passes, has been mostly closed for
OL,16,Fthe duration of the war so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
