OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio
OL,7,Fappeared to contradict these claims in
OL,8,Fan interview with Al Jazeera, saying
OL,9,Fthat the Strait of Hormuz will be kept
OL,10,Fopen "one way or another" and that US
OL,11,Fwar objectives could be achieved "in
OL,12,Fweeks, not months".
OL,14,FHe also insisted that communication
OL,15,Fbetween Tehran and Washington is
OL,16,Fongoing.
