OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FBut a spokesperson for Iran's Foreign
OL,7,FMinistry once again reiterated that no
OL,8,Fnegotiations had taken place, while
OL,9,Fconfirming that intermediaries had
OL,10,Fdelivered a set of proposals to Iran.
OL,12,FIt comes as Israel and the US launched
OL,13,Fa new barrage of strikes on Tehran, a
OL,14,Fday after Trump threatened to
OL,15,F"obliterate" Iranian energy sites if
OL,16,Fthe country did not agree to a peace
OL,17,Fdeal "shortly".
OL,19,FIsrael and US launch new wave of
OL,20,Fstrikes on Iran
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
