OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FIsrael's military said on Tuesday it
OL,7,Fhad launched a new wave of strikes on
OL,8,Fthe Iranian capital Tehran. The IDF
OL,9,Fsays the strikes targeted the
OL,10,F"infrastructure of the Iranian terror
OL,11,Fregime".
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump shared a
OL,14,Fvideo of a massive explosion without
OL,15,Fcomment on Truth Social. It appears to
OL,16,Fbe of a major strike conducted outside
OL,17,Fof the central Iranian city of Isfahan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
