PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774998182
OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FThe video appears to show a huge
OL,7,Ffireball near Mount Soffeh, an area
OL,8,Fbelieved to have military positions.
OL,9,FIran has not yet confirmed the attack.
OL,11,FIsfahan is home to one of three
OL,12,Furanium enrichment sites bombed by the
OL,13,FUS in the 12-day conflict between Iran
OL,14,Fand Israel in June. A portion of
OL,15,FIran's highly enriched uranium is
OL,16,Fbelieved to be entombed there `
OL,17,Fsomething America has suggested it
OL,18,Fcould seize with ground forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
