OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Iran continued attacks on
OL,7,Fcivilian targets, as an Iranian drone
OL,8,Fhit a Kuwaiti oil tanker in Dubai
OL,9,Fwaters, sparking a blaze that was
OL,10,Flater put out, the Dubai Media Office
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FA drone interception caused minor
OL,14,Fdamage to six homes in a residential
OL,15,Farea in Al Kharj, Saudi Arabia. The
OL,16,Fcountry's civil defence said that no
OL,17,Finjuries were reported. Al Kharj is
OL,18,Fthe site of a U.S. airbase where
OL,19,Fprevious strikes killed at least two
OL,20,Fmigrant workers and an American
OL,21,Fsoldier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
