OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FSirens were also heard in Jerusalem
OL,7,Fand loud explosions were heard not
OL,8,Flong after Israel's military warned of
OL,9,Fan incoming missile barrage from Iran.
OL,11,FFour people were wounded in Dubai
OL,12,Fafter interception debris caused a
OL,13,Ffire in an abandoned house in Al
OL,14,FBadaa, according to the Dubai Media
OL,15,FOffice.
OL,17,FIn Bahrain, authorities said warning
OL,18,Fsirens were sounded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
