OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FThe Gulf countries host US forces and
OL,7,Fbases from which the US has launched
OL,8,Fstrikes on Iran, but have not joined
OL,9,Fthe offensive strikes.
OL,11,FEyes on Kharg Island as more US
OL,12,Fassault troops head to region
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
