OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FTrump said on Monday that "great
OL,7,Fprogress is being made" in talks with
OL,8,FIran to end military operations. But,
OL,9,Fhe warned, if a deal is not reached
OL,10,F"shortly" and the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,11,Fnot immediately reopened, the US would
OL,12,Fbroaden its offensive by "completely
OL,13,Fobliterating" power plants, oil wells,
OL,14,Fand Kharg Island.
OL,16,FThe US has sent a contingent of 2,500
OL,17,Fmarines to the region, with more on
OL,18,Ftheir way. Trump also ordered 1,000
OL,19,Fparatroopers to the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
