OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774998182
OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FTrump has openly spoken about the
OL,7,Fpossibility of trying to seize Kharg
OL,8,FIsland, Iran's main oil export hub,
OL,9,Fand Iran has accused the US of using
OL,10,Fdiplomacy to stall until more troops
OL,11,Fcan be brought in.
OL,13,FThe US has already targeted military
OL,14,Fpositions on the island. Iran
OL,15,Fthreatened to launch its own ground
OL,16,Finvasion of Gulf Arab countries and to
OL,17,Fmine the Persian Gulf if US troops set
OL,18,Ffoot on its territory.
OL,20,FPeacekeepers killed in Lebanon
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
