OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FThe UN Security Council planned to
OL,7,Fconvene an emergency session on
OL,8,FTuesday after officials said three
OL,9,Fpeacekeepers in southern Lebanon had
OL,10,Fbeen killed in less than 24 hours.
OL,12,FThe UN peacekeeping mission in the
OL,13,Fregion where Israel is battling the
OL,14,FIran-backed Hezbollah did not say who
OL,15,Fwas responsible for the deaths.
OL,17,FIsrael said early Tuesday that a
OL,18,Ffurther four soldiers had been killed
OL,19,Fin its offensive in Lebanon. The
OL,20,Fdeaths bring the total number of
OL,21,FIsraeli troops killed in the war to 10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
