OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Israel's military warned
OL,7,Fthe public of an incoming missile
OL,8,Fbarrage from Iran on Tuesday, the
OL,9,Fday's first. Sirens sounded in
OL,10,FJerusalem a short while later and loud
OL,11,Fbooms were heard.
