OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FIn the UK, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer announced that he will chair
OL,8,Fan emergency Cobra meeting to look at
OL,9,F"making sure that everything that we
OL,10,Fneed to have in place, everything is
OL,11,Fmonitored and audited properly".
OL,13,FIt comes after Sir Keir told business
OL,14,Fchiefs in Downing Street on Monday
OL,15,Fthat it must be a "joint effort" to
OL,16,Ftackle the impact of the war, saying
OL,17,Fthe Government "can't do it on its
OL,18,Fown".
