OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FBosses from energy, shipping and
OL,7,Fbanking firms were invited to Number
OL,8,F10 to discuss Iran's ongoing blockade
OL,9,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, which has
OL,10,Fdisrupted a vital shipping route for
OL,11,Fthe oil and gas industry.
OL,13,FSpot prices of Brent crude, the
OL,14,Finternational standard for oil,
OL,15,Fhovered around $107 (#81.03) a barrel
OL,16,Fin early trading, up more than 45%
OL,17,Fsince the war started on February 28.
OL,19,FSearch team boards disabled Thai
OL,20,Fvessel but does not find missing crew
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
