OL,3,CTrump willing to end war without
OL,4,Creopening Strait of Hormuz, reports say
OL,6,FThe operator of a Thai cargo ship
OL,7,Fstruck by a projectile near the Strait
OL,8,Fof Hormuz last month said a search
OL,9,Fteam was able to board the vessel but
OL,10,Fdid not locate its missing three crew
OL,11,Fmembers.
OL,13,FPrecious Shipping Co., Ltd said in a
OL,14,Fstatement to the Stock Exchange of
OL,15,FThailand on Monday that all accessible
OL,16,Fareas on the Mayuree Naree ship were
OL,17,Fsearched "under challenging
OL,18,Fconditions, including the presence of
OL,19,Ffire damage, residual smoke, and
OL,20,Fflooding in the engine room."
